description: Pittsburgh inspired, Arizona desired, Steel City Pierogi is serving up your perfect street food today! Potato and cheese stuffed dumplings are a delicious way to satisfy your cravings for something filling and tasty to fuel your day. Add sour cream, bacon bits, and jalapenos for your own custom treat. Together with their hoagies, stuffed cabbage, and halushki, this food truck is sure to have something for you!
name: Steel City Pierogi
